SmallSpyder provides below functions:
  1. Spydering
     Traces specified web sites with the specified depth,
     and analyze the contents using natural language processing
     thanks to Yahoo! JLP service
     http://developer.yahoo.co.jp/webapi/jlp/ma/v1/parse.html
     
  2. Key word search
     Provides web site urls which contains specified key words.

